19 December 2018
"Agroecological Practices for sustainable Agriculture"

   "Agroecological Practices for sustainable Agriculture"

   Good agroecological practices are indispensable for the development of
   sustainable agriculture. In this book, principles, diversity and
   applications of agroecological practices for a range of systems are
   presented, transforming scientific research and participatory knowledge
   of production into practical application.
   Read more
   /

